security: Transmittal of Debrieflon Report on use of Fraudulent Interratione Travel Documentation by Cuban Intelligence.
summary: A transmittal of a debriefing report regarding Cuban Intelligence's use of fraudulent international travel documents.
summary_one_paragraph: This document is a transmittal from an unspecified sender to the Chief of Station in London, and Chief in Frankfurt, forwarding a debriefing report concerning Cuban Intelligence's utilization of fraudulent international travel documentation to facilitate passage to a local liaison service, referencing case 4819, and local liaison 24, dated July 13, 1964.
title: Transmittal of Debriefing Report on use of Fraudulent International Travel Documentation by Cuban Intelligence.
recipient: Chief of Station, London; Chief, Frankfurt
